name: Kristin Kreuk - Textual Inversion
description:
This ti is a commission of @Zorglub

Kristin Kreuk is a Canadian actress. Kreuk gained fame for her portrayal of Lana Lang in the television series "Smallville," which aired from 2001 to 2011. After "Smallville," Kreuk went on to star in the television series "Beauty & the Beast," where she played the lead role of Catherine Chandler. In addition to her television work, Kristin Kreuk has appeared in various films such as "EuroTrip," "Street Fighter: The Legend of Chun-Li," and "Space Milkshake." She has also been involved in other television projects, including the miniseries "Ben Hur" and the series "Burden of Truth," where she plays the lead character and is also an executive producer.
